import React from 'react';
import {Container, AppBar, Typography, Grow, Grid} from '@material-ui/core'; //Grid is used for a simple animation. you may not need it
import Carousel from 'react-material-ui-carousel'; //I read documentation separately
import { Paper, Button } from '@mui/material'; //to test out Carousel
